ActOld Age Security Act
SubjectMorocco - Convention on Social Security * coming into force *
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue giving notice to the general public that the CONVENTION ON SOCIAL SECURITY between the Government of CANADA and the Government of the KINGDOM OF MOROCCO, signed on July 1, 1998, will be in force as of MARCH 1, 2010.
